'''比奇溪'''（{{lang-en|'''Bitch Creek'''}}）為位在[[美國|美國]][[爱达荷州|爱达荷州]]東南方和[[怀俄明州|怀俄明州]]西方的河川。該河流是由怀俄明州西方的兩條支流：北比奇溪（North Bitch Creek）和南比奇溪（South Bitch Creek）交匯而成。途中匯集了火山口溪（Crater Creek）以及傑克松溪（Jackpine Creek）等支流後而進入愛達荷州境內。進入愛達荷州後，該河流做為[[弗里蒙特縣_(愛達荷州)|弗里蒙特縣]]與[[提頓縣_(愛達荷州)|提頓縣]]的邊界。該河流最後匯入在[[德里格士|德里格士]]西北方的[[提頓河_(愛達荷州)|提頓河]]。比奇溪長度約{{convert|15|mi}}，其中不包含該河流之支流<ref name="frenzy">(24 February 2009). [http://www.flyfishingfrenzy.com/2009/02/24/fly-fishing-bitch-creek-idaho/ Fly Fishing Idaho's Lesser Known Rivers. Bitch Creek] {{Wayback|url=http://www.flyfishingfrenzy.com/2009/02/24/fly-fishing-bitch-creek-idaho/ |date=20170426132528 }}, ''Fly Fishing Frenzy''</ref>。

該河流以前別名為堤頓河北汊（North Fork Teton River）<ref name="GNIS">{{cite gnis|title=Bitch Creek|id=377707|entrydate=June 21, 1979|accessdate=March 4, 2013}}</ref>。

該河流名稱據說來自法語的詞彙「biche」（意思為[[母鹿|母鹿]]），而該河流原名是由法國獵人命名的「Anse de Biche」<ref name="biche">[http://books.google.com/books?id=rJV8SEY3IdQC&pg=PA406&dq=%22Bitch+Creek%22+biche+unhappy&hl=en&sa=X&ei=tnCRUO6VG-2F0QGWqIGIAg&ved=0CC8Q6AEwAQ#v=onepage&q&f=false Idaho: A Guide in Word and Pictures] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=rJV8SEY3IdQC&pg=PA406&dq=%22Bitch+Creek%22+biche+unhappy&hl=en&sa=X&ei=tnCRUO6VG-2F0QGWqIGIAg&ved=0CC8Q6AEwAQ#v=onepage&q&f=false |date=20140627014610 }}, p. 406 (1937)</ref>。

